name: Utinerary
body:
Thanks for visiting! Currently, Utinerary can be downloaded. However the build is very unstable and is still a WIP. If you want to see it so far, download the .zip file. After unziping it, open the directory Youtinary-1 and run the HTML File revf.html with Google Chrome Stable.

If you see any visible bugs there is no need to report it. If it works, please give feedback at utineraryapp@gmail.com

Last Updated: 9:46 AM May 22 2016
